Class DynamicDocumentDataMapperFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.dynamicforms.domain.document.data.DynamicDocumentDataMapperFactory

  • @Service
public class DynamicDocumentDataMapperFactory
extends Object
    Central component for retrieving a DynamicDocumentDataMapper for a particular output format. Allows writing and reading document data in that format.

        public void registerMapper(@NonNull
                           @NonNull String format,
                           @NonNull
                           @NonNull Function<String,DynamicDocumentDataMapper> mapperFactory)
        Register a mapper factory for a particular format. The factory method must return a DynamicDocumentDataMapper and will receive the requested format as the single function parameter.
        Parameters:
        format - the mapper is for
        mapperFactory - for creating a new mapper instance
